#. <section class="sutta" id="sn10.4"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn10.4:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 10"
msgstr "Linked Discourses 10"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "sn10.4:0.2"
msgid "1. Indakavagga"
msgstr "1. With Indaka"

#. </p><h1>
msgctxt "sn10.4:0.3"
msgid "4. Maṇibhaddasutta"
msgstr "4. With Maṇibhadda"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "sn10.4:1.1"
msgid ""
"Ekaṃ samayaṃ bhagavā magadhesu viharati maṇimālike cetiye maṇibhaddassa "
"yakkhassa bhavane."
msgstr ""
"At one time the Buddha was staying in the land of the Magadhans at the "
"Maṇimālika tree shrine, the haunt of the native spirit Maṇibhadda."

msgctxt "sn10.4:1.2"
msgid ""
"Atha kho maṇibhaddo yakkho yena bhagavā tenupasaṅkami; upasaṅkamitvā "
"bhagavato santike imaṃ gāthaṃ abhāsi:"
msgstr ""
"Then the native spirit Maṇibhadda went up to the Buddha, and recited this "
"verse in the Buddha’s presence:"

#. </p><blockquote class="gatha"><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
#. <a class="verse-num-sc" id="verse-num-sc812"></a>
msgctxt "sn10.4:2.1"
msgid "“Satīmato sadā bhaddaṃ,"
msgstr "“It’s always auspicious for the mindful;"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn10.4:2.2"
msgid "satimā sukhamedhati;"
msgstr "the mindful prosper in happiness."

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn10.4:2.3"
msgid "Satīmato suve seyyo,"
msgstr "Each new day is better for the mindful,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn10.4:2.4"
msgid "verā ca parimuccatī”ti."
msgstr "and they’re freed from enmity.”"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts2ed" id="pts2ed1.448"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc3"></a>
#. <a class="verse-num-sc" id="verse-num-sc813"></a>
msgctxt "sn10.4:3.1"
msgid "“Satīmato sadā bhaddaṃ,"
msgstr "“It’s always auspicious for the mindful;"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn10.4:3.2"
msgid "satimā sukhamedhati;"
msgstr "the mindful prosper in happiness."

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn10.4:3.3"
msgid "Satīmato suve seyyo,"
msgstr "Each new day is better for the mindful,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn10.4:3.4"
msgid "verā na parimuccati."
msgstr "but they’re not freed from enmity."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc4"></a>
#. <a class="verse-num-sc" id="verse-num-sc814"></a>
#. VAR: sabbamahorattaṃ → sabbamahorrattiṃ (s1-3, km, mr)
msgctxt "sn10.4:4.1"
msgid "Yassa sabbamahorattaṃ,"
msgstr "But someone whose mind delights in harmlessness,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn10.4:4.2"
msgid "ahiṃsāya rato mano;"
msgstr "all day and all night,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn10.4:4.3"
msgid "Mettaṃso sabbabhūtesu,"
msgstr "with love for all living creatures—"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn10.4:4.4"
msgid "veraṃ tassa na kenacī”ti."
msgstr "they have no enmity for anyone.”"
